    "description": "<strong>这是一款克苏鲁题材的点击冒险类游戏。<br>在剧情与设定上跟B站的同名互动视频有多处不同，已经根据本游戏的交互形式做出了适配性改编。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/6dd20605514de1e4b34579485295080d.poster.avif?t=1745226317\" width=630 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/6dd20605514de1e4b34579485295080d.webm?t=1745226317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/6dd20605514de1e4b34579485295080d.mp4?t=1745226317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>黑白真人手绘美术，架空70年代时代背景。<br></li><li>没有过分的Jump scare，任何心理素质的玩家都可放心游玩。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/c10132428371acc0229c9810ddf987fc.poster.avif?t=1745226317\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/c10132428371acc0229c9810ddf987fc.webm?t=1745226317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/c10132428371acc0229c9810ddf987fc.mp4?t=1745226317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/142f0a2715d9ee3f74b14bdf80fa6e28.poster.avif?t=1745226317\" width=630 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/142f0a2715d9ee3f74b14bdf80fa6e28.webm?t=1745226317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/142f0a2715d9ee3f74b14bdf80fa6e28.mp4?t=1745226317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>有守密人陪伴着你。<br></li><li>对话采用插图式的人物特写或物品特写，仔细观察，也许会发现什么。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/fb4354e7039f62a700f85bccde0fb824.poster.avif?t=1745226317\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/fb4354e7039f62a700f85bccde0fb824.webm?t=1745226317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/fb4354e7039f62a700f85bccde0fb824.mp4?t=1745226317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/18610b787712ec77c29b16af3837404b.poster.avif?t=1745226317\" width=630 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/18610b787712ec77c29b16af3837404b.webm?t=1745226317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/18610b787712ec77c29b16af3837404b.mp4?t=1745226317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>通过匹配道具，与NPC展开对话以推进剧情。<br></li><li>通过分配角色技能资源探索游戏中秘密。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/e1a8418efe98e5755aadef852ab8f348.poster.avif?t=1745226317\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356330/extras/e1a8418efe98e5755aadef852ab8f348.webm?t=1745226317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.